bilingual.source: He also made a video in space.
bilingual.target: 他还在太空中拍了视频。
视频主要是关于什么的？
很多人观看了这段视频。

Which poem is mentioned in the video?

bilingual.target: 把你的视频分成短片段拍摄。

bilingual.target: 你会用什么来拍摄视频？

bilingual.source: Decide the details of filming the video.
What sports are mentioned in the video?
bilingual.target: 视频中提到了哪些运动？

bilingual.source: Yang Liwei made a video in space.

list.abstract: 英文名称：Video：视频 指0～10兆赫范围内的频率。用以生成或转换成图像。在电视技术中，又称为电视信号频率，所占频宽为0～6兆赫。广泛应用于电视、摄录像、雷达、计算机监示器中。 现在的2008年的数字视频处理技术正在蓬勃发展，并且2008年的奥运会将采用全部的数字直播。
video，英语单词，主要用作名词、形容词、动词，作名词时意为“[电子]视频；录像，录像机；电视”，作形容词时意为“视频的；录像的；电视的”，作动词时意为“录制”。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me. This is my video log here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不好意思，这是我的视频日志。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I guess this is my last video log.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想这是我最后的视频日志了。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. This is video log 12. Time's 21:32.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，这是第12号视频日志，时间是21点32分。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you for the video. That wasn't what I expected to see.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢你们做的视频，我真没想到。

yingyinNormal.en: The first part of your conversation was, in fact, pre-recorded video. Easily arranged. It's a Skype call.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们的前半段对话其实是提前录好的视频，非常好弄。是视频通话。

yingyinNormal.en: And please take down the online video of your client playing our song.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有请你们把网上你们委托人的表演视频撤下。

yingyinNormal.en: Am I in your kitchen with you? No. Then you're not shooting a video with Joe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在在你的厨房里吗？不在。所以你没在跟乔拍视频。

yingyinNormal.en: Max, why are you taking calls from Chiandra? We have to do my video.
yingyinNormal.zh: Max 你干嘛要接Chiandra的电话啊? 要开始帮我录视频了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, there's a video message. It's address to the whole crew. Play it. Come on, guys.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，有个视频信息是，是发给全队的。播放来一下, 各位。

yingyinNormal.en: And you remember how to video chat? Yes, yes. With the phone and the buttons and the agony.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有你记得怎么视频聊天吗？记得，手机按键还真苦恼。

yingyinNormal.en: The future of my pants hinges on the video pitch. The tone needs to be sad and pathetic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我未来的裤子就指望这条视频了，我要用很可怜很可悲的语气。

yingyinNormal.en: Cause you know that's all fake. It's all done on a computer? It's like that video, what is it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些可都是假的，是电脑特效，就像那个视频一样，什么来着？

yingyinNormal.en: You had great interviews, great video. You nailed it, Ben. Congrats. You're an intern.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你面试得很好，你的视频也很棒，恭喜你，你通过了。本，你现在是个实习生了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, dad, check out this video. It's a teacup pig playing a piano. I saw that. Andy sent it to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 老爸，来看这个视频，一头茶杯猪在弹钢琴。我看过了，安迪给我发的。

yingyinNormal.en: Override the surveillance video and CCTV systems. Ba-bam. And we are in. It's child's play.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后重写监控视频和闭路电视监控系统，叭嘣，我们进去了。斯麦利想出来的。

yingyinNormal.en: What a good choice. Mummy. And a video tape of your mummies and Daddies, when they were little. Oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你选的东西不错！还有一盘录像带，这是你们爸爸妈妈。小时候录的视频。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't want to waste a Saturday night Watching some video. Let's just stay home and rent a movie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不想把一个大好的周六晚上浪费在看视频上，我们待在家里租个电影看吧。

yingyinNormal.en: We're going to show you a segment of the three-minute video now, but please be warned, the following contains graphic descriptions and disturbing content. Viewer discretion is advised.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们会向你们展示三分钟视频里的一段，要提醒各位的是，接下来的视频包含着露骨的叙述以及可能令人不安的部分。请观众酌情观看。

yingyinNormal.en: My fashion blog is blowing up. I started doing these live video chats, and now I have over 50,000 subscribers!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的时尚博客人气暴涨，我搞起了视频聊天秀，现在我的频道有五万多订阅者！

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, two things, a movie is a video, and the only reason you don't want to go to grandpa's is because you're avoiding Andy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 两件事，电影也是视频，还有你不想去外公家就是因为你害怕见到安迪。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The late psychologist Nalini Ambady asked participants to watch silent 10-second <highlight>video</highlight> clips of professors and to rate the instructor's overall effectiveness.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 已故心理学家参观者观看十秒钟有关教授的无声影视片段并对其授课效果进行整体评价。

examination_example.sentence: Other agencies would protect against anti-competitive behavior, such as a broadband-providing conglomerate like AT&T favoring its own <highlight>video</highlight>-streaming service
examination_example.sentence_trans: 其他机构会保护自己不受反竞争行为的影响，比如像AT&T这样的宽带提供商，支持自己的视频流服务。

examination_example.sentence: They're part of a bunch of celebrities starring in a new <highlight>video</highlight> for World Environment Day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们是一群明星中的一员，为世界环境日拍摄了一段新视频。
